19#include "CustomData.h"
20
21namespace ZXing {
22namespace QRCode {
23
24/**
25* Meta-data container for QR Code decoding. Instances of this class may be used to convey information back to the
26* decoding caller. Callers are expected to process this.
27*/
28
29class DecoderMetadata : public CustomData
30{
31 bool _mirrored;
32
33public:
34 explicit DecoderMetadata(bool mirrored) : _mirrored(mirrored) {}
35
36 /**
37 * @return true if the QR Code was mirrored.
38 */
39 bool isMirrored() const {
40 return _mirrored;
41 }
42};
43
44} // QRCode
45} // ZXing
